{"tid":1088150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動物園猩猩真的是「工讀生」　遊客怒：讓小孩失望太荒唐","createTime":"2019-04-02T00:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T02:15:12.000Z","uid":7232,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3372179eddbdd1e4b334bd0d04e79ad53c503304","tid":1088150,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3998/d3998584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3998%2Fd3998584.jpg&h=329c9e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲江蘇的動物園竟然真的由工讀生扮演動物。（圖／翻攝自江蘇省淹城野生動物世界微博）<br />\n<br />\n記者林彥臣／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n當動物園的動物做出類似人類行為的時候，常常會被網友笑稱，「工讀生別鬧了喔，快出來」。沒想到在大陸江蘇的一間動物園還真的是由工讀生扮演動物，讓不少遊客感到相當失望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3998/d3998583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3998%2Fd3998583.jpg&h=38599728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸江蘇省淹城野生動物世界為了應景愚人節，推出「真假動物」的活動，找來了2位工作人員穿上道具服扮演猩猩。有些遊客對此感到不悅表示，「偌大的動物園竟沒有真猩猩嗎」、「光天化日之下為何讓人扮演的猩猩譁眾取寵？」不少家長對於這種讓小孩失望的荒唐行為感到不滿。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友認同這樣的活動，在江蘇省淹城野生動物世界微博上表示，「我覺得超級可愛啊」、「工作人員模仿得很精髓嘛，有點厲害啊」、「你們也太可愛了吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3998/d3998582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3998%2Fd3998582.jpg&h=f4f397b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇省淹城野生動物世界在微博上表示，有朋友說今日在我園猩猩館看見「新物種」，留言表示很氣憤，這誤會大了，這是專門為遊客朋友們準備的互動節目，演員身著猩猩服裝，在館内時而坐著時而盪鞦韆，目的是給大家歡樂，没想到有人會生氣呢。這大熱天，演員也很辛苦呢！大家愚人節快樂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190402/1413234.htm?from=fb_et_news&amp;fbclid=IwAR0PviQC3PUI5QDnEY3vWFXlHRcsCt3sm6lTNx7_Q1PZ99iuy1d1QJgtMFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190402%2F1413234.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_news%26fbclid%3DIwAR0PviQC3PUI5QDnEY3vWFXlHRcsCt3sm6lTNx7_Q1PZ99iuy1d1QJgtMFc&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m64Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=21697e3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190402/1413234.htm?from=fb_et_news&amp;fbclid=IwAR0PviQC3PUI5QDnEY3vWFXlHRcsCt3sm6lTNx7_Q1PZ99iuy1d1QJgtMFc</a>"},{"pid":"b45351740685ba6443cc8ccbcd9023a52a57ceb2","tid":1088150,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:22:17.000Z","msg":"都話係人扮"},{"pid":"21baae716405055bbc48529e9fc02c6dcb5def9d","tid":1088150,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"愚人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3249b46d21118e35d8916fea009062a15434ba95","tid":1088150,"uid":172278,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:42:59.000Z","msg":"入閘機都係<br />\n夏天嗰時冇冷氣<br />\n熱死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f823b2a74eb8c94f5868e5e9ecd005a3a324b34","tid":1088150,"uid":71243,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3249b46d21118e35d8916fea009062a15434ba95","tid":1088150,"uid":172278,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:42:59.000Z","msg":"入閘機都係<br />\n夏天嗰時冇冷氣<br />\n熱死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"巴打你加油，我做左七年閘機，岩岩上星期經理覺得我表現良好升左我做波板糖人"},{"pid":"c84f5fda863d81e71577e40bd478f13d97b68ab9","tid":1088150,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2f168f63cb5c653c8830df02f6ec667ad20225","tid":1088150,"uid":92145,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f823b2a74eb8c94f5868e5e9ecd005a3a324b34","tid":1088150,"uid":71243,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3249b46d21118e35d8916fea009062a15434ba95","tid":1088150,"uid":172278,"like":14,"dislike":3,"